  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 180 Celsius.",
    "Heat olive oil in a skillet over medium heat and sauté garlic until fragrant.",
    "Add sliced ovoli-mushroom and cook until golden, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in spinach and cook until wilted, then remove from heat.",
    "In a bowl, whisk heavy cream, yuzu zest, lemon juice, and sea salt until smooth.",
    "Layer half the mushroom mixture in a baking dish, top with half the gouda and walnuts.",
    "Pour half the cream mixture over the layer, then repeat with remaining mushroom mixture, gouda, and walnuts.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes until cheese is bubbly and golden, let rest 5 minutes before serving."
